timing_use_ver..._model_netlist(25.10)  timing_use_ver..._model_netlist(25.10)

Name
       timing_use_verilog_for_model_netlist

Syntax
       timing_use_verilog_for_model_netlist

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Allows  you  to  choose  whether  to write the scope and boundary model
       netlists in Verilog format instead of binary.

       When set to true, the software will use Verilog format for saving model
       nets.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

